    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/d6c09675ba4d8a1bb017f76648036ffe.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/96fa9078d1dd8caa5f7ed1b749f4bac8.avif?t=1752842527\" width=614 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为帝国的领导者，您必须收集硬币，以调动军队、升级省份并向将军表示忠诚。如果您的钱达到零。<strong>您输了</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有这一切的目标是扩大您的省份，同时保持同胞的支持，他们将通过您的行动失去或获得对您的领导的信任。硬币来自该地区的公民。他们越快乐，他们就会生产出越多的硬币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您还可以从各地区招募士兵，或者您可以聘请艺术家和地方法官来修改该地区公民的支持。显然，这每回合都会花费您的钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >省份距离帝国中心越远，他们给您的支持就越少。您可能会达到一个非常遥远的地步，以至于无论您做什么，各省总是处于叛乱的边缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果某个地区公民的支持达到零，该地区就会叛乱并停止向您提供资金和新兵。您必须惩罚它并让叛军为此付出代价。如果你的所有公民都不再支持你，<strong>你就输了</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/1061cffba1bfe7c7251a4863d4f70bd2.avif?t=1752842527\" width=614 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/eca1e6b3db8af8da6c6556e51951f4f9.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/d6c09675ba4d8a1bb017f76648036ffe.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/506e850d6916c9b5876690883f44a28e.avif?t=1752842527\" width=614 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将军们每次取得胜利都会在人民中赢得威望，在某个时候，他们会要求报酬，以在您的指挥下感到满意。如果您不付钱给他们，他们就会背叛您，并试图到达首都夺取权力。如果将军叛乱并征服首都。<strong>你输了</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是“野蛮人”地区不会停滞不前，他们每回合都会发展并积累士兵，让您花费更多的士兵和金钱来征服他们。如果您的军团在战斗中失败，您可能会支付赎金或死亡。<strong>你输了</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些地区可能会发展得如此之快，以至于它们成为一个帝国，向其附近扩张并挑战您的权力。这些帝国可以从您手中夺取省份，甚至征服您的祖国并摧毁您的帝国主义梦想。如果敌对帝国征服了首都。<strong>你输了</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永远记住自己生命的时间限制。死亡降临到我们所有人身上。如果你达到回合限制，你就会因年老而死。<strong>你输了</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/eca1e6b3db8af8da6c6556e51951f4f9.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/d6c09675ba4d8a1bb017f76648036ffe.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有征服整个地图才能<strong>你赢了</strong>，你将作为征服者被世世代代铭记</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/e5463ea05e22abe758e1266e68341204.avif?t=1752842527\" width=614 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037110/extras/eca1e6b3db8af8da6c6556e51951f4f9.webp?t=1752842527\" width=615 height=32 /></span></p>",
